<p class="ql-align-center">他们换装不换心，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">退伍不褪色，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">爱岗敬业，忠于职守，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在平凡的岗位上，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">继续书写退役军人新风采！</p>
